metadata.name: The Horseman Club #1
metadata.description: The Horseman Club is a distinctive collection of 5,555 art pieces that lie in the ERC-721. Each one of this tokens is unique, indomitable and rules his own life. Your Horseman NFT represents a vote inside the web 3.0 community through a DAO system. Also being a Horseman gives you access to special giveaways, monthly events and a lot more. Everything will start with a club that will be customized by the community and constructed at Bali. Visit www.thehorsemanclubnft.com for more details.
